fields.name: ProvisioningState
fields.description: Current state of this QueryPack: whether or not is has been provisioned within the resource group it is defined. Users cannot change this value but are able to read from it. Values will include Succeeded, Deploying, Canceled, and Failed.

fields.name: QueryPackId
fields.description: The unique ID of your application. This field cannot be changed.

fields.name: TimeCreated
fields.description: Creation Date for the Log Analytics QueryPack, in ISO 8601 format.

fields.name: TimeModified
fields.description: Last modified date of the Log Analytics QueryPack, in ISO 8601 format.
